### Format (format.go)

```go
// Format represents an output format.
type Format int

const (
    FormatJSON  Format = iota
    FormatYAML
    FormatTable
)

// FormatModels serializes a slice of ModelInfo in the given format.
func FormatModels(w io.Writer, models []ModelInfo, f Format) error { ... }

// FormatModel serializes a single ModelInfo in the given format.
func FormatModel(w io.Writer, model ModelInfo, f Format) error { ... }
```

YAML serialization: a minimal write-only YAML encoder (~50 lines) that handles
the flat ModelInfo struct. No external dependency needed — we only write YAML,
never read it. The encoder handles: string, int, bool, *float64 (nil → omit),
[]Modality, and Modalities struct.

